  <brief_title>Increasing Smoking Cessation Counselling in Primary Care Using a Chronic Disease Management System</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Cluster Randomized Controlled Pilot Trial of the Effect of a New, Improved Smoking Cessation Management Module, Compared With Use of the Standard Version of Such a Management Module, on Smoking Counselling Initiation and Continuation Rates in Primary Care Practices Currently Using P-PROMPT Chronic Disease Management System in Ontario</official_title>
