  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This pilot study will determine the feasibility of studying a new smoking cessation
      management module in an existing chronic disease management system. The new module is
      intended to help healthcare providers deliver more smoking cessation counselling to their
      patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
